### 📅 WEEK 1: Complete All Backend APIs (May 20–25)

> **Goal:** Finish ALL remaining Edge Functions, test every API via Postman, have a fully working backend.

#### Day 1 (Tue May 20) — Fix Current Issues + Payroll API
- [x] Fix auth middleware (service_role bypass)
- [x] Deploy attendance Edge Function with geofencing
- [ ] Run `006_attendance_fix.sql` in Supabase SQL Editor
- [ ] Test attendance geofencing in Postman (inside/outside fence)
- [ ] Build **Payroll Edge Function** (`/functions/v1/payroll`)
  - `POST /payroll` → Generate monthly payroll for all guards
  - `GET /payroll` → List payroll records (filter by month, guard, status)
  - `GET /payroll?id=X` → Salary slip detail
  - `PUT /payroll?id=X&action=approve` → Approve payroll
  - Salary formula: `(base/total_days × present) + overtime - penalties - uniform - advances`

#### Day 2 (Wed May 21) — Recruitment + Uniforms APIs
- [ ] Build **Candidates Edge Function** (`/functions/v1/candidates`)
  - `POST` → Add candidate
