  - `PUT ?id=X` → Update candidate status
  - `POST ?id=X&action=convert` → Convert candidate → guard record
- [ ] Build **Uniforms Edge Function** (`/functions/v1/uniforms`)
  - `POST` → Issue uniform item to guard
  - `GET` → List uniform items (filter by guard, payment status)
  - `PUT ?id=X` → Update payment status / amount paid
- [ ] Test both via Postman

#### Day 3 (Thu May 22) — Inspections + Notifications APIs
