## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **1. Firebase vs Supabase Auth?**
> The SRS mentions Firebase OTP for auth, but current Edge Functions use Supabase Auth. Which do you want to use? Supabase has built-in phone OTP — simpler to integrate. Firebase would need separate setup.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **2. React Native or Expo?**
> SRS says React Native (Expo). Should we use Expo Go for development or bare workflow? Expo Go is faster for development but has limitations with native modules.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **3. Admin Web Dashboard?**
> Do you also want a web-based admin dashboard (React/Next.js) in addition to the mobile app? Or is mobile-only sufficient for Phase 1?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **4. Test Data — Real locations?**
> Should the seed data use real Patna locations (with actual GPS coordinates) for testing geofencing? This would make Postman testing more realistic.

