## Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Firebase OTP setup delays | Use Supabase built-in phone OTP as fallback |
| Camera/GPS permissions issues | Test on real devices early (Day 12) |
| Payroll calculation edge cases | Write unit tests for salary formula |
| App Store rejection | Follow platform guidelines from Day 1 |
| Geofence accuracy on low-end phones | Add 20m tolerance buffer |

